    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A boon-giving hand-gesture, representing bestowing of gifts. The hand is extended downward with the palm outward, as if offering something to a devotee; an object of offering may be held in the hand. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
